Sorry, but doing a CR in PoG with protectors up is not a real difficult endeavor and never has been. Doing one in Fear on a full spawn was always harder than it ever was doing one in PoG. The protectors are the only thing that made PoG difficult in the first place and they were supposed to have been there the whole time. Arguing that they shouldn't come back because they make the zone harder is silly because the zone is much too easy without them. They don't actually make the zone harder, they just return it to the difficulty it is supposed to have. If you don't feel it is worth it, go to any of the other zones you mentioned. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380">Qaman</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
